 Create a directory named: apache-php that containe :
	
 dockerfile and apache-php file and a directory named www contain index.php file

code:

- Docker  build  –t=” mywebsite” .       ( the . To tell as to  build from the directory)

     NOW THE IMAGE IS build and  READY LETS RUN IT :
     
     code: 
     
 - docker run –d –p 8080:80 mywebsite
	
